        <div xml:id="TK1271">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>karappiṉuṅ kaiyikan tollāniṉ ṉuṇka </l>
<l> ṇuraikka luṟuvatoṉ ṟuṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Though you would conceal (your feelings), your painted eyes would not, for, transgressing (their bounds), they tell (me) something.</l>
            </lg>
